de: Political-Military Steering Committee on Partnership for Peace Trust Fund Project Proposal for Building Integrity in the Security Sector (Phase II), Note by the Chairman - 31-03-2010 - Ausführungs- und Finanzverwaltungsabkommen zwischen der Schweizerischen Eidgenossenschaft, Polen, dem Vereinigten Königreich und dem Internationalen Sekretariat der NATO betreffend des Fonds für spezielle Verwendungszwecke im Bereich der Verstärkung der Integrität und der Reduktion von Korruptionsrisiken in den Verteidigungsinstitutionen
en: Political-Military Steering Committee on Partnership for Peace Trust Fund Project Proposal for Building Integrity in the Security Sector (Phase II), Note by the Chairman - 31-03-2010 - Executing Agent Agreement and Financial Management Agreement between Switzerland, Poland and the United Kingdom and the NATO office of financial control for the support of the building integrity and reducing corruption risk in defence establishments trust fund (PfP Trust Fund Building Integrity)
fr: Political-Military Steering Committee on Partnership for Peace Trust Fund Project Proposal for Building Integrity in the Security Sector (Phase II), Note by the Chairman - 31-03-2010 - Accord d'exécution et accord de gestion des finances entre la Confédération suisse, la Pologne, le Royaume-Uni et le Secrétariat international de l'OTAN concernant le fonds d'affectation spéciale en matière de renforcement de l'intégrité et de réduction du risque de corruption dans les institutions de défense
